# ─── web/output: generated at build time by EspWebUI ─────────────────────────
# These files are auto-generated from web/html/, web/js/ and web/css/.
# They must NOT be excluded because EspWebUI reads them during the build
# to produce the gzip_*.h header files embedded in the firmware.
# Only the sim.json and index.html (GitHub Pages preview) can be excluded
# if you don't use GitHub Pages:
# web/output/index.html
# web/output/sim.json
